      <title>渣打银行将在英国银行承诺后向碳信用公司提供首笔商业债务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/stanchart-offer-first-commercial-debt-carbon-credit-firm-after-ba-commitment-2024-09-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行向路透社透露，在英国航空公司同意从项目开发商 UNDO 预先购买超过 4,000 吨碳排放额度后，渣打银行将向一家技术型碳去除公司提供首笔商业债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/stanchart-offer-first-commercial-debt-carbon-credit-firm-after-ba-commitment-2024-09-11/</guid>
