      <title>裕信银行如何收购德国商业银行股份以在德国扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/how-unicredit-swept-up-stake-commerzbank-bid-grow-germany-2024-09-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二欧洲时间已近傍晚，投资者的疑虑正在加剧。德国政府试图通过市场配售出售德国商业银行股票，表面上看来这是一项简单的任务，但这一计划却遭遇了阻碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/how-unicredit-swept-up-stake-commerzbank-bid-grow-germany-2024-09-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 20:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
